  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      We hypothesize that misexpression of vascular endothelial growth factor (VEGF) in the
      Cerebrospinal fluid of preterm infants can be used as a biomarker to predict the risk for
      developing white matter damage.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
